"1/2 cup cider vinegar","1/2 cup water","2 teaspoons sugar","3/4 cup thinly sliced red bell pepper rings","3/4 cup thinly sliced yellow bell pepper rings","3/4 cup thinly sliced green bell pepper rings","1/2 cup thinly sliced English cucumber","1/2 cup thinly sliced onion","3 tablespoons chopped fresh dill, divided","1 pound 93% lean ground beef","3/8 teaspoon kosher salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","  Cooking spray","4  (1/2-ounce) slices reduced-fat colby-Jack or cheddar cheese","1/4 cup canola mayonnaise","4  whole-wheat hamburger buns, toasted"